data.description: Charming 3-bed, 2-bath home in Brookstone, Brookwood - great for first-time buyers. Built-in 2006, this 1,697 sqft home boasts a spacious master bedroom, a split floor plan, and an efficiently maintained HVAC system. Features a cozy breakfast room-kitchen combo, laundry room, and a two-car garage.
